{"TopicId":201429,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Why is my rocket tipping?","CreatedByName":"jonahk3","CreatedById":210971,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-02T22:29:04Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"jonahk3","CreatedById":210971,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-02T22:29:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;border:0px;color:#878a8c;font-size:medium;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022border:0px;font-size:20px;padding:0px 5px 0px 0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ch1 style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\nWhy is my rocket tipping?\n\u003C/h1\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;border:0px;color:#878a8c;font-size:medium;padding:5px 16px 5px 0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022border:0px;color:#1a1a1b;font-size:14px;padding:0px 0px 1px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px 0px .25em;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\nOK so I know this a commonly asked question, but I cannot figure out why my rocket is tipping. Immediately after launch (less than 5 secs) it begins turning in a random direction (different each time), until its facing down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px .25em;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\nThe purpose of the rocket is to bring some mining equipment to the surface of Ike.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px .25em;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\nHere are some pictures\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://preview.redd.it/b6t77u7svtq61.png?width=404\u0026amp;format=png\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;s=59b1ffdf21e73da2ba1161e521a4e49bfc6564fb\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022border:0px;color:inherit;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022r/KerbalAcademy - Why is my rocket tipping?\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022116.58\u0022 style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022 width=\u0022404\u0022 src=\u0022https://preview.redd.it/b6t77u7svtq61.png?width=404\u0026amp;format=png\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;s=59b1ffdf21e73da2ba1161e521a4e49bfc6564fb\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px .25em;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://preview.redd.it/84n8cvytvtq61.png?width=200\u0026amp;format=png\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;s=8af8e77e1ab0ff60f91a79ec7beb496ae5ade097\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022border:0px;color:inherit;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022r/KerbalAcademy - Why is my rocket tipping?\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022186.50\u0022 style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022 src=\u0022https://preview.redd.it/84n8cvytvtq61.png?width=200\u0026amp;format=png\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;s=8af8e77e1ab0ff60f91a79ec7beb496ae5ade097\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px .25em;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://preview.redd.it/7lk35u7wvtq61.png?width=265\u0026amp;format=png\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;s=831632fca5f7490230d7058d951e905ae436dda5\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022border:0px;color:inherit;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022r/KerbalAcademy - Why is my rocket tipping?\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022160.75\u0022 style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022 width=\u0022265\u0022 src=\u0022https://preview.redd.it/7lk35u7wvtq61.png?width=265\u0026amp;format=png\u0026amp;auto=webp\u0026amp;s=831632fca5f7490230d7058d951e905ae436dda5\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px .25em;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\nI have removed the fairing that would be at the top usually.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px .25em;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px .25em;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\nThe first is a pic of the whole rocket, the second the mining part with the hinge inward (where it would be for takeoff), and the third the hinge outward (Where it would be for mining)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px .25em;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\nHere is the craft file -\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://easyupload.io/deijvl\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022border:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003Ehttps://easyupload.io/deijvl\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px .25em;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\nAll help is appreciated, thanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px 0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\nIf you also need the LoadMeta file for the craft (I am new to this), I can edit the post just tell me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px 0px;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\nI am using the Breaking Ground DLC\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ben J. Kerman","CreatedById":204948,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-02T23:20:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm, is it bending, or just flat out falling over while remaining rigid as a whole? If it is bending before falling, then you just might need to use autostrut on some of the parts. If it is just falling over, then it could be a weight distribution issue, or much more likely, something else I don\u0027t know about. Sorry if this is no help at all, but check if this works (Unless you already used autostrut or\u00A0normal struts.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-03T09:33:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks like too much mass at the bottom end. Those SRBs seem overkill for that payload so I\u2019d downsize those first. Second I\u2019d \u2018bulk up\u2019 the upper stage with more fuel to push the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003ECoM\u003C/abbr\u003E up. Finally I\u2019d ditch the fins on the upper part as drag higher up is undesirable. Plus I\u2019d stick to just 1 fin per side as 3 just adding more mass.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIf it\u2019s still not playing nicely, stay vertical for as long as you need before doing a gravity turn. You\u2019ll use more fuel but it should resist flipping higher up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPS make sure there\u2019s plenty of reaction wheels as well.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OHara","CreatedById":162784,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-03T14:03:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223948400\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201429\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221617402544\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210971\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jonahk3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 hours ago, jonahk3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022border:0px;padding:.8em 0px .25em;vertical-align:baseline;\u0022\u003E\nIf you also need the LoadMeta file for the craft (I am new to this), I can edit the post just tell me.\u00A0\u00A0I am using the Breaking Ground DLC\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe do not need the .loadmeta file to try your craft, but we do\u00A0need to have all the mods for parts you use (KOS for the KAL9000) .\u00A0 I have used\u00A0KOS so I reactivated it to try your craft, but you might want to upload a version with the KAL9000 removed so more people can try it.\u00A0 Letting people try the craft is a very good idea, because otherwise people are just guessing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor me, the rocket flew fine with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E off, but it turned off course with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E on.\u00A0 As you uploaded it, the control point is the Probodobodyne in the miner probe, which is upside down, so it would steer backwards.\u00A0 You can set an option to have the Probodobodyne look up when it is steering the booster.\u003Cimg alt=\u00228l1U8Y6.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002252.67\u0022 height=\u0022505\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/8l1U8Y6.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}